Nominations close Monday, June 12, 2023. One Mile.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: AA SWEET VICTORY prompted the pace for three quarters then took command at the top of the stretch and held on for the win. RS JEWEL CROWN was unhurried around the first turn then moved up down the backstretch, angled out to three wide in upper stretch and was a game second. UPTOWN LADY ARABELLA tracked the leaders through the final turn then moved out to four wide in the stretch, passed a tired on and proved to be best of the rest. WMA BIG BABY went to the front to set a pressured pace for three quarters then was headed at the quarter pole and tired. VAZILLA SV was through after a half and jogged in. WIKISPEEDIA saved ground down the backstretch but was distanced and eased.
